<body class="mybgimg aboutus fontstyle">
<img src="<%= asset_path('aboutus.png') %>", class="infotitle">
<h1 class="zhtitle">關於我們</h1>
<div class="contentinfo">
    <div class="d-flex flex-row col-12 about">
        <div class="stu col-lg-9 col-md-12 col-sm-12">
            <div class="stu-say p-2">
                <p>唉～</p>
                <p>這個⽉⼯讀薪資何時下來呢？</p>
                <p>餐廳那邊有確實登錄好我今天工讀時數嗎？</p>
                <p>BY 學生 哈利Ｘ特</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
        
    <div class="d-flex flex-row-reverse col-12 about">
        <div class="sta col-lg-9 col-md-12 col-sm-12">
            <div class="staff-say p-2">
                <p>工作忙翻了！</p>
                <p>電腦⼜遠！</p>
                <p>即時登錄⼯讀學⽣時數好麻煩啊！</p>
                <p>新工讀學⽣⼀個⼀個 key 好累啊！</p>
                <p>BY 教職員 石Ｘ卜</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="d-flex flex-row col-12 about justify-content-center">
        <h2>不用再煩惱了！</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="d-flex flex-row col-12 about justify-content-center">
        <div>
            <p>Oh My Wage 團隊的</p>
            <p>霍格華茲學院工讀薪資系統，</p>
            <p>給您「即時、方便 、簡單」的科技體驗，</p>
            <p>享受資訊往來就在彈指之間！</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="d-flex flex-row col-12 about justify-content-center">
        <h2>成員</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="d-flex justify-content-center worker-int flex-column">
        <div class="p-2 d-flex worker-int">
            <div class="p-2 col-lg-4 col-md-12 col-sm-12">
                <%= image_tag('river.png', class:'workerimg') %>
            </div>
            <div class="p-2 worker-say col-lg-8 col-md-12 col-sm-12">
                <p>
                    你必須很努力，才能看起來毫不費力。
                </p>
                <p>
                    看似輕鬆的背後，有著看不盡的付出。
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="p-2 d-flex worker-int">
            <div class="p-2 col-lg-4 col-md-12 col-sm-12">
                <%= image_tag('axel.png', class:'workerimg') %>
            </div>
            <div class="p-2 worker-say col-lg-8 col-md-12 col-sm-12">
                <p>
                    從不同的觀點思考，
                </p>
                <p>
                    用好奇心探索世界！
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="d-flex justify-content-center flex-column">
        <div class="p-2 d-flex worker-int">
            <div class="p-2 col-lg-4 col-md-12 col-sm-12">
                <%= image_tag('joan.png', class:'workerimg') %>
            </div>
            <div class="p-2 worker-say col-lg-8 col-md-12 col-sm-12">
                <p>
                    你不一定要變得很厲害，
                </p>
                <p>
                    才能開始；
                </p>
                <p>
                    你要開始，才能變得很厲害！
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="p-2 d-flex worker-int">
            <div class="p-2 col-lg-4 col-md-12 col-sm-12">
                <%= image_tag('patrick.png', class:'workerimg') %>
            </div>
            <div class="p-2 worker-say col-lg-8 col-md-12 col-sm-12">
                <p>
                    渴求知識，喜歡探索，
                </p>
                <P>
                    享受思考後發現新世界的興奮。
                </P>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="center-block">
    <%= link_to "回到首頁", '/', class: 'btn btn-gray btn-lg' %>
</body>